Package edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.templates

Class Summary
Alpha6 The VM is configured to automatically run this class, and to call the functions corresponding to each mode, as described in the IterativeRobot documentation.
Belt Controls the belt which picks balls up off of the floor.
Drive Drive system with two Jaguars driven in tank drive.
Gamepad Holds a joystick and simplifies gamepad functions.
Manipulator Class that contains two jaguars that control the motors in the arm
SafeJaguar Jaguar capable of setting speeds relative to values received from the PID controller in either PWM or CAN networks.
Wiring Holds constants for the robot in the form of static variables.
